data.description: Welcome to your new home nestled in the serene community of Orcutt! Situated on a tranquil cul-de-sac, this charming residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and ample living space, perfect for families seeking comfort and convenience.Upon arrival, you'll be greeted by a spacious lot adorned with lush fruit trees, offering a picturesque setting for outdoor enjoyment. The property features a  RV parking.Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed floor plan, highlighted by a cozy family room and inviting living room, ideal for relaxing or entertaining guests. The expansive dining room provides the perfect backdrop for hosting gatherings and holiday celebrations.For added convenience, there is a half bathroom inside the laundry room ensures quick cleanups after outdoor adventures or meals with loved ones. Recent updates to the bathrooms and kitchen elevate the home's appeal, blending modern amenities with timeless charm.Located in a highly desirable school district. Don't miss your chance to experience the epitome of comfortable living in this peaceful Orcutt retreat. Schedule your showing today and make this dream home yours!
